  "root_text": {
    "sn2.24:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 2.24 ",
    "sn2.24:0.2": "3. Nānātitthiyavagga ",
    "sn2.24:0.3": "Ghaṭīkārasutta ",
    "sn2.24:1.1": "Ekamantaṁ ṭhito kho ghaṭīkāro devaputto bhagavato santike imaṁ gāthaṁ abhāsi: ",
    "sn2.24:2.1": "“Avihaṁ upapannāse, ",
    "sn2.24:2.2": "vimuttā satta bhikkhavo; ",
    "sn2.24:2.3": "Rāgadosaparikkhīṇā, ",
    "sn2.24:2.4": "tiṇṇā loke visattikan”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:3.1": "“Ke ca te ataruṁ paṅkaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:3.2": "maccudheyyaṁ suduttaraṁ; ",
    "sn2.24:3.3": "Ke hitvā mānusaṁ dehaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:3.4": "dibbayogaṁ upaccagun”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:4.1": "“Upako palagaṇḍo ca, ",
    "sn2.24:4.2": "pukkusāti ca te tayo; ",
    "sn2.24:4.3": "Bhaddiyo khaṇḍadevo ca, ",
    "sn2.24:4.4": "bāhuraggi ca saṅgiyo; ",
    "sn2.24:4.5": "Te hitvā mānusaṁ dehaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:4.6": "dibbayogaṁ upaccagun”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:5.1": "“Kusalī bhāsasī tesaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:5.2": "mārapāsappahāyinaṁ; ",
    "sn2.24:5.3": "Kassa te dhammamaññāya, ",
    "sn2.24:5.4": "acchiduṁ bhavabandhanan”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:6.1": "“Na aññatra bhagavatā, ",
    "sn2.24:6.2": "nāññatra tava sāsanā; ",
    "sn2.24:6.3": "Yassa te dhammamaññāya, ",
    "sn2.24:6.4": "acchiduṁ bhavabandhanaṁ. ",
    "sn2.24:7.1": "Yattha nāmañca rūpañca, ",
    "sn2.24:7.2": "asesaṁ uparujjhati; ",
    "sn2.24:7.3": "Taṁ te dhammaṁ idhaññāya, ",
    "sn2.24:7.4": "acchiduṁ bhavabandhanan”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:8.1": "“Gambhīraṁ bhāsasī vācaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:8.2": "dubbijānaṁ sudubbudhaṁ; ",
    "sn2.24:8.3": "Kassa tvaṁ dhammamaññāya, ",
    "sn2.24:8.4": "vācaṁ bhāsasi īdisan”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:9.1": "“Kumbhakāro pure āsiṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:9.2": "vekaḷiṅge ghaṭīkaro; ",
    "sn2.24:9.3": "Mātāpettibharo āsiṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:9.4": "kassapassa upāsako. ",
    "sn2.24:10.1": "Virato methunā dhammā, ",
    "sn2.24:10.2": "brahmacārī nirāmiso; ",
    "sn2.24:10.3": "Ahuvā te sagāmeyyo, ",
    "sn2.24:10.4": "ahuvā te pure sakhā. ",
    "sn2.24:11.1": "Sohamete pajānāmi, ",
    "sn2.24:11.2": "vimutte satta bhikkhavo; ",
    "sn2.24:11.3": "Rāgadosaparikkhīṇe, ",
    "sn2.24:11.4": "tiṇṇe loke visattikan”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:12.1": "“Evametaṁ tadā āsi, ",
    "sn2.24:12.2": "yathā bhāsasi bhaggava; ",
    "sn2.24:12.3": "Kumbhakāro pure āsi, ",
    "sn2.24:12.4": "vekaḷiṅge ghaṭīkaro. ",
    "sn2.24:13.1": "Mātāpettibharo āsi, ",
    "sn2.24:13.2": "kassapassa upāsako; ",
    "sn2.24:13.3": "Virato methunā dhammā, ",
    "sn2.24:13.4": "brahmacārī nirāmiso; ",
    "sn2.24:13.5": "Ahuvā me sagāmeyyo, ",
    "sn2.24:13.6": "ahuvā me pure sakhā”ti. ",
    "sn2.24:14.1": "“Evametaṁ purāṇānaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:14.2": "sahāyānaṁ ahu saṅgamo; ",
    "sn2.24:14.3": "Ubhinnaṁ bhāvitattānaṁ, ",
    "sn2.24:14.4": "sarīrantimadhārinan”ti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn2.24:0.1": "Linked Discourses 2.24 ",
    "sn2.24:0.2": "3. Various Sectarians ",
    "sn2.24:0.3": "With Ghaṭīkāra ",
    "sn2.24:1.1": "Standing to one side, the godling Ghaṭīkāra spoke this verse in the Buddha’s presence: ",
    "sn2.24:2.1": "“Seven mendicants reborn in Aviha ",
    "sn2.24:2.2": "have been freed. ",
    "sn2.24:2.3": "With the complete ending of greed and hate, ",
    "sn2.24:2.4": "they’ve crossed over clinging to the world.” ",
    "sn2.24:3.1": "“Who are those who’ve crossed the bog, ",
    "sn2.24:3.2": "Death’s dominion so hard to pass? ",
    "sn2.24:3.3": "Who, after leaving behind the human body, ",
    "sn2.24:3.4": "have risen above celestial yokes?” ",
    "sn2.24:4.1": "“Upaka and Palagaṇḍa, ",
    "sn2.24:4.2": "and Pukkusāti, these three; ",
    "sn2.24:4.3": "Bhaddiya and Bhaddadeva, ",
    "sn2.24:4.4": "and Bāhudantī and Piṅgiya. ",
    "sn2.24:4.5": "They, after leaving behind the human body, ",
    "sn2.24:4.6": "have risen above celestial yokes.” ",
    "sn2.24:5.1": "“You speak well of them, ",
    "sn2.24:5.2": "who have let go the snares of Māra. ",
    "sn2.24:5.3": "Whose teaching did they understand ",
    "sn2.24:5.4": "to cut the bonds of rebirth?” ",
    "sn2.24:6.1": "“None other than the Blessed One! ",
    "sn2.24:6.2": "None other than your instruction! ",
    "sn2.24:6.3": "It was your teaching that they understood ",
    "sn2.24:6.4": "to cut the bonds of rebirth. ",
    "sn2.24:7.1": "Where name and form ",
    "sn2.24:7.2": "cease with nothing left over; ",
    "sn2.24:7.3": "understanding this teaching, ",
    "sn2.24:7.4": "they cut the bonds of rebirth.” ",
    "sn2.24:8.1": "“The words you say are deep, ",
    "sn2.24:8.2": "hard to understand, so very hard to wake up to. ",
    "sn2.24:8.3": "Whose teaching did you understand ",
    "sn2.24:8.4": "to be able to say such things?” ",
    "sn2.24:9.1": "“In the past I was a potter ",
    "sn2.24:9.2": "in Vebhaliṅga called Ghaṭīkāra. ",
    "sn2.24:9.3": "I took care of my parents ",
    "sn2.24:9.4": "as a lay follower of Buddha Kassapa. ",
    "sn2.24:10.1": "I refrained from sexual intercourse, ",
    "sn2.24:10.2": "I was chaste, spiritual. ",
    "sn2.24:10.3": "We lived in the same village; ",
    "sn2.24:10.4": "in the past I was your comrade. ",
    "sn2.24:11.1": "I am the one who understands ",
    "sn2.24:11.2": "that these seven mendicants have been freed. ",
    "sn2.24:11.3": "With the complete ending of greed and hate, ",
    "sn2.24:11.4": "they’ve crossed over clinging to the world.” ",
    "sn2.24:12.1": "“That’s exactly how it was, ",
    "sn2.24:12.2": "just as you say, Bhaggava. ",
    "sn2.24:12.3": "In the past you were a potter ",
    "sn2.24:12.4": "in Vebhaliṅga called Ghaṭīkāra. ",
    "sn2.24:13.1": "You took care of your parents ",
    "sn2.24:13.2": "as a lay follower of Buddha Kassapa. ",
    "sn2.24:13.3": "You refrained from sexual intercourse, ",
    "sn2.24:13.4": "you were chaste, spiritual. ",
    "sn2.24:13.5": "We lived in the same village; ",
    "sn2.24:13.6": "in the past you were my comrade.” ",
    "sn2.24:14.1": "“That’s how it was ",
    "sn2.24:14.2": "when those friends of old met again. ",
    "sn2.24:14.3": "Both of them are evolved, ",
    "sn2.24:14.4": "and bear their final body.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "sn2.24:0.3": "Ghaṭīkārasutta → ghaṭikārasuttaṁ (sya2ed) ",
    "sn2.24:4.1": "palagaṇḍo → phalagaṇḍo (bj, sya-all, pts1ed, pts2ed, mr) ",
    "sn2.24:4.4": "bāhuraggi ca saṅgiyo → bāhudantī ca piṅgiyo (bj); bāhudakkhi ca siṅgiyo (cck); bāhuraggi ca siṅgiyo (sya1ed, sya2ed); bāhuraggi ca piṅgiyo (pts1ed, pts2ed) "
  },
